title: Liberty's Maddie Capuano is lehighvalleylive Girls Volleyball Player of the Week
text:
Maddie Capuano (4) (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By Kyle Craig | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 18, 2015 6:05 PM 
GIRLS VOLLEYBALL PLAYER OF THE WEEK Maddie Capuano (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) 
Maddie Capuano , Liberty 
The senior is known for her scoring on the hardwood come winter, as a record-setting 3-point shooter for the Hurricanes. However, sheâ€™s recognized here for her capabilities as a distributor. 
Capuano registered 119 assists in victories over Dieruff, Bethlehem Catholic and Freedom over the last week. She also had 21 digs combined in the wins over the Golden Hawks and Patriots. 
Honorable mention : Sr. OH Kristen Betterman , Notre Dame; So. OH Leanna Deegan , Easton; Sr. S Kristin Krause , Parkland; Sr. S Brooke Lichty , Nazareth; So. MH Grace Mittl , Liberty; Sr. OH Katrina Ruggiero , Nazareth.
